Multi (posix) thread proxy implementation in C.
This is currently an initial exercise for later implementation of an anonymous proxy

The Makefile here is for Linux.  
 - If compiling on Solaris, add "-lsocket".
 - For mac/os remove "-lnsl" (i.e., remove $(xFlag))


